description: "Obriy AI specializes in AI-driven customer support automation through its flagship platform, SURE. The platform leverages advanced large language models (LLMs) to create intelligent AI agents capable of handling up to 90% of customer inquiries with expert-level accuracy. SURE integrates seamlessly with various communication channels such as web chats, Instagram, Telegram, WhatsApp, and Zendesk, as well as CRM systems like Salesforce and KeyCRM, enabling centralized management of customer interactions. The platform is built for scalability and supports businesses of all sizes, making it suitable for enterprises seeking to optimize customer service operations. SURE harnesses proprietary technology, including semantic segmentation, prioritized retrieval systems, and governed retrieval-augmented generation (RAG), ensuring responses are precise, contextual, and based on verified data. Its intelligent knowledge base allows agents to access critical information instantly, creating structured and reproducible answers. Notable features include real-time query escalation to human team members for complex issues, round-the-clock support, and built-in KPI analytics for continuous improvement. With a focus on automation, SURE reduces support costs, boosts team efficiency, and enhances customer satisfaction by providing fast, accurate responses and seamless omnichannel experiences. Obriy AI emphasizes ease of implementation, offering effortless setup supported by their team, with integration timelines ranging from one day to a few weeks depending on complexity. Their technology is engineered for flexibility, enabling custom integrations with additional systems to meet specific business needs. Overall, Obriy AI positions itself as a leader in transforming customer service through cutting-edge automation and intelligent AI agents tailored to enterprise growth and operational efficiency."

Its platform helps leaders improve their skills by delivering personalized feedback aligned with their company's values and team dynamics. Ogma addresses the shortcomings of traditional leadership training, which is often generic, expensive, and lacks real-time applicability. Using advanced natural language processing (NLP) technology, Ogma analyzes conversation patterns, engagement levels, and subtle nuances such as tone and context. The AI then offers actionable guidance on areas like trust-building, psychological safety, active listening, and coaching mindset. Designed for managers at all experience levels, Ogma seamlessly integrates with popular video conferencing platforms and works unobtrusively during regular 1:1s. Key features include progress tracking, value-aligned growth, and balanced feedback, empowering leaders to continuously improve without disrupting workflows. The platform promotes measurable impact, with early users reporting increased confidence and stronger team connections. Notably, Ogma emphasizes privacy, ensuring all insights are constructive and focused on leadership growth rather than performance monitoring. By embedding leadership development into daily routines, Ogma enables organizations to foster resilient, high-performing teams while reinforcing their unique cultures and values.
